thread.title: Jenny

author: Jenny
title: Jenny
text: The only problem that I had with my experience was that the trees came the night before I left on a week's vacation, in a snow storm, so I wasn't able to plant right away. However, they are really nice looking trees, and they were very well packaged, so I was able to leave them for the week and found them to be just fine when I got back. We'll see how they grow, but so far, so good.
